---
---

<section class="bg-white py-24 md:py-36">
  <div class="container-x">
    <div class="grid items-start gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-20">

      <!-- LEFT: sticky pitch -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 lg:sticky lg:top-28 lg:self-start">
        <span class="eyebrow">
          <span class="h-px w-6 bg-gold"></span>
          The real problem
        </span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-medium leading-[1.05] tracking-tight md:text-5xl lg:text-[3.25rem]">
          Here's why your business is struggling to get more leads.
        </h2>

        <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink md:text-xl">
          Your business is struggling because your marketing strategy is outdated.
        </p>

        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-ink/65 md:text-lg">
          We're in the age of AI. That means you need to start targeting for both AI
          <span class="font-medium text-ink">(GEO)</span> and humans. If your business isn't showing up where your customers are searching, someone else's is.
        </p>

        <div>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-ink/65 md:text-lg">
            In order to get meaningful results, you need to show up in <span class="font-medium text-ink">all parts of Search</span> — to take up as much Google search real estate as possible.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3">
            {[
              'Local Service Ads',
              'PPC Ads',
              'Local Pack',
              'Organic Content',
              'Traditional Listing',
            ].map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-base text-ink/80">
                <span class="flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gold/10">
                  <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
                    <path d="M2 5.5L4 7.5L8 3" stroke="#987622" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                  </svg>
                </span>
                {item}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-ink/65 md:text-lg">
          Additionally, it's crucial to have a strong digital presence not only on Google but also on
          <span class="font-medium text-ink">Social Media Platforms</span>,
          <span class="font-medium text-ink">LLMs</span> (ChatGPT, Gemini, Perplexity AI, and Claude AI)
          and any other industry-relevant directories to maximize exposure for your business.
        </p>

        <!-- Pullquote -->
        <blockquote class="relative rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-[#FBF8EF] p-8 md:p-10">
          <span class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-4 left-8 font-display text-7xl leading-none text-gold/20 select-none">&ldquo;</span>
          <p class="relative text-base leading-relaxed text-ink md:text-lg">
            Don't let SEO agencies fool you. Website traffic isn't an indicator your website is doing well.
            A website's purpose isn't traffic — it's <span class="font-semibold text-ink">conversion</span>.
          </p>
          <footer class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="h-px w-8 bg-gold"></span>
            <div>
              <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Jack He</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-ink/50">Owner, Rumeira</div>
            </div>
          </footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT: image + body content (taller column, drives the scroll) -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-black/[0.06] shadow-[0_40px_100px_-30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)]">
          <img
            src="/images/James M. McGill Ad v2.webp"
            alt="Rumeira digital marketing — search everywhere optimization example"
            width="900"
            height="1100"
            class="w-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
